                "invention-title": [
                    "Equipment for producing hydrogen and synthesizing ammonia through seawater in-situ desalination",
                    "一种海水原位淡化制氢合成氨的设备"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides seawater in-situ desalination hydrogen production and ammonia synthesis equipment which comprises a water electrolysis hydrogen production system, a forward osmosis membrane filtration system, an oxygen production and collection system, a hydrogen production and collection system and an ammonia synthesis system. Water molecules in the seawater are transmitted to one side of the electrolyte through the forward osmosis membrane, so that in-situ desalination of the seawater is realized. The seawater desalination process and the electrolyte supplementing process of the electrolytic hydrogen production equipment are organically fused, and the high chemical potential energy of the electrolyte and the transmembrane transportation process of the forward osmosis process based on the osmotic pressure difference are combined, so that a fresh water resource is provided for water electrolysis hydrogen production; hydrogen and nitrogen generated by seawater electrolysis can be subjected to in-situ reaction to directly prepare the green ammonia, so that the problems of shortage of water resource supply, complex investment, operation and maintenance of seawater desalination equipment, high cost, difficulty in hydrogen absorption and the like in the current hydrogen production process can be effectively solved, and an effective path can be provided for green ammonia production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种海水原位淡化制氢合成氨的设备，包括：电解水制氢系统、正渗透膜过滤系统、氧气生产收集系统、氢气生产收集系统以及氨合成系统，正渗透膜两侧的海水与电解液渗透压差的作用下，海水中的水分子透过正渗透膜传输至电解液一侧，实现海水的原位淡化。本发明将海水淡化过程与电解制氢设备的电解液补充过程有机融合，将电解液的高化学势能与正渗透工艺基于渗透压差的跨膜运输过程相结合，为电解水制氢提供淡水资源，并能将海水电解制备产生的氢气与氮气原位反应直接制备成绿氨，能够有效解决当前制氢工艺存在的水资源供应紧张、海水淡化设备投资运行维护复杂及成本高、氢气消纳困难等问题，并能够为绿氨生产提供有效路径。"
                }
            ]
